"{\"uid\": \"newseu.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-10-Olympic-redemption-Ireland-gymnast-climbs-back-to-be-Paris-champion-1vXqS3SNCjm-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peter Oliver in Paris  Copied  Ireland's Rhys McClenaghan's Olympic gold at the gymnastics pommel horse event in Paris is redemption for his Tokyo disappointment three years ago.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 205, \"end\": 217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Oliver_(painter)\", \"score\": 0.6896481230480077, \"rank\": 0.45000000000002693, \"text\": \"Peter Oliver\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Oliver_(painter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Oliver_(painter)\"}, {\"begin\": 221, \"end\": 226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999683473112, \"rank\": 3.165262219972203e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 236, \"end\": 243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9363095423490568, \"rank\": 0.06801762527049053, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 246, \"end\": 262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhys_McClenaghan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rhys McClenaghan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhys_McClenaghan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhys_McClenaghan\"}, {\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999683473112, \"rank\": 3.165262219972203e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9194110261282268, \"rank\": 0.087617392873097, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A momentary lapse of concentration saw the Newtownards man fall from the horse and out of contention for a medal at the last Games.\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 428, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newtownards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.97514707376478e-22, \"text\": \"Newtownards\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newtownards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newtownards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He arrived in Paris, a three-time European and two-time world champion, ready to set the record straight.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 532, \"end\": 537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999683473112, \"rank\": 3.165262219972203e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He told CGTN Europe his Olympic gold is the culmination of years of dedication.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lifetime of work paying off in one little moment.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's a very powerful thing to have happened to you,\\\" said McClenaghan.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 831, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think the human brain is meant to comprehend something like that fully.\\\"\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even the very best can fall'  He remains philosophical about the fall in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 992, \"end\": 997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9194110261282268, \"rank\": 0.087617392873097, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Su Weide fell twice from the high bars during the team competition in Paris.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999885705925098, \"rank\": 5.2902479988346625e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999683473112, \"rank\": 3.165262219972203e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the nature of gymnastics.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even the very best can fall, and fall multiple times,\\\" McClenaghan added.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We all know it's a possibility.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just about who can hold their nerve in that moment and not make those big errors.\\\"\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He will return to Newtownards, a town in County Down, Northern Ireland, with his gold and every intention of using his own success to inspire future generations.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newtownards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.97514707376478e-22, \"text\": \"Newtownards\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newtownards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newtownards\"}, {\"begin\": 1354, \"end\": 1365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Down\", \"score\": 0.9999998497739966, \"rank\": 1.5022607702427893e-07, \"text\": \"County Down\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Down\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Down\"}, {\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999996557563, \"rank\": 2.829346320604093e-10, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My hometown has never seen an Olympic medal before.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is going to be super special, bringing back a gold one.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope to use it in the most responsible manner possible,\\\" said the Olympian.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1658, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999996952520187, \"rank\": 2.987965802885055e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In my mind, that's to inspire a younger generation.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But then also everybody in that town and everybody in the country, hopefully, will be inspired to just work hard.\\\"\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1836, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mutual respect  Gymnastics is an event that captures even the casual viewer's imagination at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1856, \"end\": 1866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9001584217394799, \"rank\": 0.10887343009634322, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everybody from across the world in gymnastics, including the Chinese, we all have this mutual respect for each other,\\\" McClenaghan said highlighting the unity gymnasts share.\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2010, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9432335751333577, \"rank\": 0.05995689181236246, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We all know how difficult it is just to get to the Olympic Games so when we see each other, it's a pleasure and we congratulate each other.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We welcome each other into the village, into the gymnastics halls and it's been a very nice experience shared with the other gymnasts.\\\"\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2402, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McClenaghan held up his gold medal, showing its beauty up close, confirming it is just as heavy as one would expect it to be.\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's no surprise he had to take it off to sleep the night after his victory as it was too heavy.\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2627, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He intends to be back at the Olympics in LA in 2028, hoping to try his hand at other Gymnastic events as well as the pommel horse.\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the best of CGTN every Friday  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": []}]}"